androidx.test.orchestrator.instrumentationlistener

Class OrchestratedInstrumentationListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • RunListener
      • androidx.test.orchestrator.instrumentationlistener.OrchestratedInstrumentationListener

  • public final class OrchestratedInstrumentationListener
extends RunListener
    A RunListener for the orchestrated instrumentation to communicate information back to the OrchestratorService. Not to be attached to AndroidTestOrchestrator itself.
